<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Terms & Conditions | BioBrain</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/desktopStyle.css" />
  
</head>
<body class="view-pages-desktop-terms">

  <%- include('../../partials/desktop/header') %>

  <div class="disclaimer-container">
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>

    <button class="collapsible">1. Acceptance of Terms</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>By accessing or using BioBrain, you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, you must not use the platform.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">2. Use of Platform</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>The platform is provided for educational and entertainment purposes only. Users must not misuse the platform or its content.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">3. Account Registration</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Users may be required to register an account. You are responsible for maintaining confidentiality of login credentials and activity associated with your account.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">4. User Conduct</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Users must not engage in unlawful, abusive, or disruptive behavior on the platform. Harassment or misuse may lead to suspension or account termination.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">5. Intellectual Property</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>All content, logos, designs, and quizzes on BioBrain are the property of BioBrain and protected under copyright laws. Users must not reproduce or distribute without permission.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>The platform and content are provided “as is” without warranties of any kind. BioBrain does not guarantee accuracy or reliability of content.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">7. Limitation of Liability</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>BioBrain is not liable for any damages, losses, or consequences arising from use of the platform, quizzes, or content.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">8. Modifications</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>BioBrain may modify the Terms & Conditions at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
    </div>

    <button class="collapsible">9. Governing Law</button>
    <div class="content">
      <p>These Terms & Conditions are governed by the laws applicable in India. Disputes shall be subject to the courts in India.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="btn-home">Back to Home</a>
  </div>

  <%- include('../../partials/desktop/footer') %>

  <script>
    // Collapsible sections toggle
    const collapsibles = document.querySelectorAll(".collapsible");
    collapsibles.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener("click", () => {
        btn.classList.toggle("active");
        const content = btn.nextElementSibling;
        if (btn.classList.contains("active")) {
          content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + "px";
        } else {
          content.style.maxHeight = null;
        }
      });
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>